i HATE HATE HATE HATE summer school! (but its my fault im here)

my daddy said were going to move within a year or so....do you know how much bawls that sucks? ive never moved! ive lived in stupid circle-land since i was born! in the same house, same friends, same things to do.
and where were suposedly "moving" you wonder? get this.....missurri. double-u-tee-eff huh? its not even a place to me! not that dothan isnt bumfu**nowhere either...but gah!

went to panama city the day b4 yesterday. with tiffany, and her family..her mom was drunk everynight from 6-3. so i was very free. which in a way turned out bad..eh hem. but anywho, she (while plastered) told me to invite my "boyfriend" ((((john paley guys)))to spend the night. walked across front beach road to use the payphone. (she wouldnt let me use her phone). half of my big toe is literally gone because of that walk. (i slipped on glass, and toe+concreate=bad). going back to get medical crap, she made me walk her down to the front desk, so she wouldnt fall. getting there she threw pens and brochures at the poor dude-kid at the front desk. (something about her sheets being dirty). i had to push her out with me. upstairs i wrote in my diary "tabitha is plastered"...and sumthing about feeling like "a whore" because of how the guys there treated me and tiff. went back down to get a bandaide. came back to find those words scribbled out. -personal! private! diary!- stupid drunk douch face................next day, we go to a water park. some guy feels me up in the water. got a sunburn. go back to the condo- where i go up to the room to find john and his friend waiting. it was the best thing in the world to see him there! because, i missed home. and hes part of it i find. we swam. he left.

.....wow, he went all the way to panama to see me for an hour. haha..sweet.

then that night we ate out, where i ordered  "ragoni" salad! ewwww eww ew. and in the parking lot my mommy picked me up and saved me! yay mommy!
4 nights of freedom...i miss rules!

party tonight...later
